Solutions







Search for Solutions


Search 









From ocean to orbit and everywhere in between, Harris provides mission-critical solutions to connect, inform and protect the world. Harris is a proven leader in tactical communications, geospatial systems and services, air traffic management, environmental solutions, avionics and electronic warfare, and space and intelligence. Harris delivers its innovative solutions through its three business segments: Communication Systems, Space and Intelligence Systems and Electronic Systems.


