3 Harris Corp. Product Manager Salaries 

Browse Harris Corp. Salaries by Job Title →

Harris Corp. Product Managers earn $93,000 annually, or $45 per hour, which is 9% higher than the national average for all Product Managers at $85,000 annually and 42% higher than the national salary average for ​all working Americans. The highest paid Product Managers work for Empirix at $188,000 annually and the lowest paid Product Managers work for hhgregg at $25,000 annually.






